data.description: Are you looking for country living not too far from the city? Then look at this two-story home with a private drive, situated on over an acre of land, offers a perfect blend of country living and convenience to city amenities. Scenic deck overlooking the property, providing a serene outdoor space for relaxation and entertaining. There is a large barn with a workshop, loft, and a half bath. Storage shed at the back of the property as well.
